# Project Structure and Entry Points

This repo is a monorepo with `backend/` (NestJS) and `frontend/` (Next.js App Router).

- Frontend entry: `frontend/src/app/layout.tsx` and route files under `frontend/src/app/`
- Backend entry: `backend/src/main.ts`, root module `backend/src/app.module.ts`

Important frontend directories:
- UI building blocks: `frontend/src/components/ui/`
- App UI patterns: `frontend/src/components/app-ui/` (e.g., `page-header`, `page-wrapper`, `confirmation-modal`, `pagination`)
- Feature pages: `frontend/src/components/pages/**`
- Services and hooks: `frontend/src/services/**`
- Constants and URLs: `frontend/src/constants/**`
- Hooks: `frontend/src/hooks/**`

API docs live at [api-doc.md](mdc:api-doc.md) at repo root and are the source of truth for service types and endpoints.

